              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Late August through to mid-November is Pullenvale's strongest window. The suburb shows at its best in spring, school-catchment buyers are making decisions for the following year, and longer evening light suits acreage inspections. A secondary window runs from late February to mid-April, driven by upgraders committing to lifestyle changes in the new year."
            }
